  ^cyan;New in version 6.0.1422 ^reset;

  (edwardspec, Kherae, anoobindisguise, Zarra, sayter, Challicus, Moxy, Rylasasin)

  -- Research --
  * Refined passive gain script to be more concise
  * Removed the 25+ minute bonus from higher tier worlds (6+). Instead, they will simply provide a flat bonus of +6.
  * Set-based Research bonuses no longer apply on every tick, and instead have a success rate based a roll of 1d10+Research Bonus versus a target number of 8.

  -- Assets --
  * added new objects: 3 Totem Poles, Wooden Lectoral, Water Barrel, Gold Chest, Golden Display Armour, Golden Armed Display Armour, Gold Medieval Chandelier, Golden Medieval Globe, Golden Medieval Street Lamp, Iron Ornate Chandelier, Gold Ornate Chandelier, Silver Candle, Silver Chalice, Silver Hourglass, Silver Ornate Chandelier, Silver Royal Candles and Silver Royal Throne.
