  * Exceptional Combs now work in both the Honey Jarrer and Honey Jarring Machine
  * Sulphuric Dark biomes now use the appropriate biome type as their core biome
  * transmutation matrix no longer consumed when 'upgrading' items at or above max level.
  * extra stats window now rounds crit chance to one decimal place.
  * Wind Arrays should accurately output their power levels
  * adjusted consumer scripts to address incorrect power draining rates
  * Mantizi mech body properly appears once in the Engineering tree
  * corrected a few weapon modiifers where if the item was held by itself in the right hand, it would penalize the user, instead of giving the single-wield bonus.
  * corrected mastery bonuses only applying for the last weapon type compared
  * corrected an error kill/hit damage listeners where the counter would only consider monsters, not NPCs.

